        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 9. Distribution of Solanum americanum Mill in the Old World." , "Figure 8. Solanum americanum Mill A Habit B Leaves and young inflorescence C Buds and flowers D Mature, shiny black fruits with reflexed calyx lobes (A, D Knapp et al. 10210; B Knapp et al. 10205; C Knapp et al. 10360). Photos by S. Knapp." , "Figure 7. Solanum americanum Mill A Habit B Detail of abaxial leaf surface C Detail of adaxial leaf surface D Branch with inflorescence E Leaf F Dissected flower G Fruit (A-D, F-G Cremers 8084; E Farrugia 2773). Drawing by R. Wise." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/218712" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/218711" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/218710" .

